In <Bxz4An.FtH@chinet.chi.il.us> schneier@chinet.chi.il.us (Bruce Schneier) writes:

>I second the proposal for the creation of sci.crypt.politics.  Let's get the
>politics off of this newsgroup!

No. Let's give this a few weeks to blow over. It will move out of sci.crypt of
its own accord. Especially if we (occasionally) remind people to move.

I've already seen LOTs of discussion about the privacy and political
ramifications in other existing groups. We don't need a new one. Alternately,
someone might want to create an alt group for the duration.
